=Max&amp;rft.aulast=Henrion&amp;rft.date=1991&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=AI+magazine&amp;rft.pages=64&amp;rft.volume=12.4&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Faaaipress.org%2Fojs%2Findex.php%2Faimagazine%2Farticle%2Fdownload%2F919%2F837&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite id="CITEREFShweHorvitz1991" class="citation">Shwe, Michael A.; et al. (1991), "Probabilistic diagnosis using a reformulation of the INTERNIST-1/QMR knowledge base", <i>Methods of information in Medicine</i>, <b>30.4</b>: 241\xe2\x80\x93255</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEric+Horvitz&amp;rft.atitle=Probabilistic+diagnosis+using+a+reformulation+of+the+INTERNIST-1%2FQMR+knowledge+base&amp;rft.au=Horvitz%2C+Eric&amp;rft.aufirst=Michael+A.&amp;rft.aulast=Shwe&amp;rft.date=1991&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Methods+of+information+in+Medicine&amp;rft.pages=241-255&amp;rft.volume=30.4&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite id="CITEREFHorvitzCooperHeckerman1989" class="citation">Horvitz, Eric; Cooper, G.F.; Heckerman, D. (August 1989), <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://research.microsoft.com/~horvitz/reflect.htm">"Reflection and action under scarce resources: Theoretical principles and empirical study"</a>, <i>Proceedings of the IJCAI</i>: 1121\xe2\x80\x931127</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEric+Horvitz&amp;rft.atitle=Reflection+and+action+under+scarce+resources%3A+Theoretical+principles+and+empirical+study&amp;rft.au=Cooper%2C+G.F.&amp;rft.au=Heckerman%2C+D.&amp;rft.aufirst=Eric&amp;rft.aulast=Horvitz&amp;rft.date=1989-08&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Proceedings+of+the+IJCAI&amp;rft.pages=1121-1127&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fresearch.microsoft.com%2F~horvitz%2Freflect.htm&amp;rft_val_fmt